@endnode

@node kakkah25 "DayDream BBS - ARexx - Supported Commands - INTCOMMAND"

INTCOMMAND <Command>
This command makes it possible to run DayDream's main menu commands
from arexx-doors (only internal, no doors)

Example:
IntCommand "N S A"

@endnode

@node kakkah26 "DayDream BBS - ARexx - Supported Commands - FIFOEXECUTE"

FIFOEXECUTE <Command>
Executes amigados command and routes output to DD.
Some control codes in command are available:

    %N = Node, %H = Handle, %R = Real name, %S = Screen length

Example:
FifoExecute "Lha a ram:sihi DayDream:#? -r"

@endnode

@node kakkah27 "DayDream BBS - ARexx - Supported Commands - WRITELOG"

WRITELOG <String>
Writes specified text to the logfile.
Some control codes in command are available:

            %A = ARQ Report
            %B = Baudrate
            %D = Date
            %H = Handle
            %L = Location
            %N = Node
            %O = Organization
            %S = Security
            %T = Time
            %U = Real name

Example:
WRITELOG "%U aka %H proved that he's gay!"

@endnode

@node kakkah28 "DayDream BBS - ARexx - Supported Commands - EDITFILE"

EDITFILE <file>

         Edit ascii file with selected editor.

Example:
EDITFILE "Ram:Pussy"

@endnode

@node rexx5 "DayDream BBS - ARexx - Debugging"

Debugging
~~~~~~~~~
